data.description: This beautiful 2-story home sits on a sprawling, flat third of an acre property with gorgeous trees and shade in the highly desirable but rarely available Encino Park subdivision.  This home boasts an abundance of natural light, vaulted ceilings, and wide-plank flooring throughout the downstairs. The kitchen updates include quartz countertops, modern cabinet hardware, and stainless steel appliances. The second living area opens to the kitchen and backyard along with a fireplace and adjacent wet bar. The oversized master bedroom and bath has dual vanities and a separate shower and tub.  Come see this home before the summer rush begins!
